<main class="container">
    <!-- Background Video -->
    <video src="./img/beach.mp4" muted loop autoplay class="back_video"></video>
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About-FAQ</h1>
        
        <!-- Accordion Component -->
        <div class="accordion mt-4" id="accordionFAQ">
            <!-- Section 1 -->
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                        What kind of animals do you shelter?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordionFAQ">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        We shelter a variety of animals including dogs, cats, rabbits, birds, and small mammals. Our goal is to provide a safe and loving environment for all animals in need.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Section 2 -->
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                        How can I adopt an animal from your shelter?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordionFAQ">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        To adopt an animal from our shelter, you can visit our facility during adoption hours and meet the animals available for adoption. Our staff will assist you in finding the perfect match for your family.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Section 3 -->
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        Do you offer spaying/neutering services?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionFAQ">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Yes, we offer spaying and neutering services for all animals adopted from our shelter. It is an essential part of responsible pet ownership and helps control pet overpopulation.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- End of Accordion Component -->
    </div>
</main>